name: Stranger In Gensokyo: Elden Dream Origin

description:
[Entry for  Touhou Fan Game Jam 8]

Definitely not based off any soulslike or anything.

Controls

Movement - Arrow Keys
Dodge Roll - Left Shift
Attack - Z Key
Jump - X Key
